42 (A) The crisis call center system and crisis hotline center described in subsections (4) and (5)
43 of this section; and
44 (B) To the extent that the crisis call center system and crisis hotline center are fully funded,
45 the expansion and ongoing funding of mobile crisis intervention teams.
